data.title: Episode 2613 (30 October 2003)
data.meta_description: Lisa's world begins to crumble around her. Ash makes a crucial discovery as Paul and Janine's secret is exposed. Lisa Fowler - Lucy Benjamin Den Watts - Leslie Grantham Dennis Rickman - Nigel Harman Janine Butcher - Charlie Brooks Paul Trueman - Gary Beadle Barry Evans - Shaun Williamson Patrick...
data.text:
Dennis finds Lisa drinking. Den arrives and gives her the sack. Dennis tells Ronny that Tariq was dealing.

The Ferreiras put a rat in Gavin's flat.

Paul and Janine are trapped in bed upstairs at the B&B when Patrick and Yolande come back unexpectedly.

Lisa approaches a little girl and gets knocked over by the mother and falls down drunk in the street in front of everyone. She goes home and looks at a bottle of pills.
